{
  "stem": "3012.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't care about Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had lists.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had lists, because eventually, the gendarmes-- and these were the most evil people you can imagine, the Hungarian gendarmes-- they were-- they were [? brigandists. ?] They were-- they were torturers.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were beasts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I don't have any way of knowing whether there was a retribution after the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The gendarmes picked up the people, eventually, who were suspected of having hidden something-- some valuable that belonged to them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did not steal it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It belonged to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they subjected them to horrendous torture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They picked up my grandfather from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father, my uncle, and my aunt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I cannot tell you what they did to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gradually-- I believe it was in April-- there was a decree.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to wear a yellow star sewn on this-- on the left side of the clothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Without that, you couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- in case it was not stitched properly, they could arrest you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] anything could have happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In May-- sometimes in May, because I remember we were already in the ghetto on the day of my birthday.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They herded us in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we stayed there until the sixth of June.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a decree.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a decree that in 24 hours, or 48 hours, you-- you have to-- you have to find a place because this part of town will become a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other part of town will also be a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you must go, or else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't even say or else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
